Dialogue: 3,0:21:37.95,0:21:39.75,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}喂喂　先等等
Dialogue: 3,0:21:39.95,0:21:42.14,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}太刺激的內容
Dialogue: 3,0:21:42.55,0:21:46.26,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}放到最後再說吧
Dialogue: 3,0:21:46.46,0:21:50.55,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}現實中滿是不如意
Dialogue: 3,0:21:50.86,0:21:55.16,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}那就都塞到瓶子裡
Dialogue: 3,0:21:55.75,0:21:58.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}準備好參加派對了嗎?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:58.32,0:22:00.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}不等你了哦
Dialogue: 3,0:22:00.85,0:22:04.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}另一個故事就要開始了
Dialogue: 3,0:22:05.07,0:22:07.25,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}無數氣泡呼呼冒出
Dialogue: 3,0:22:07.35,0:22:09.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}無數氣泡啵啵破裂
Dialogue: 3,0:22:09.75,0:22:13.06,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}生活就像汽水
Dialogue: 3,0:22:13.84,0:22:16.25,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}無論是爸爸媽媽的事
Dialogue: 3,0:22:16.35,0:22:18.55,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}還是悶在心底的回憶
Dialogue: 3,0:22:18.62,0:22:22.95,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}都會化作氣泡消失掉
Dialogue: 3,0:22:23.45,0:22:25.54,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}哭泣憂愁又煩惱
Dialogue: 3,0:22:25.75,0:22:27.75,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}無數往事多紛擾
Dialogue: 3,0:22:28.04,0:22:31.45,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}都沒關係的
Dialogue: 3,0:22:32.15,0:22:34.65,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}所有往事盡懷抱
Dialogue: 3,0:22:34.65,0:22:36.90,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}塞進瓶子使勁搖
Dialogue: 3,0:22:36.90,0:22:41.16,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}噗嗤全部釋放　大家一起歡笑
Dialogue: 3,0:22:41.25,0:22:44.45,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}咕嚕嚕　瞬間滿是氣泡
